➜博君一笑cp被拆？那个传闻中搞定王一博的白富美究竟是谁？
http://www.sohu.com/a/333941281_407929	33071
<p class="ql-align-justify">昨天晚上迎来了今夏爆火的《陈情令》的大结局，嗑“博君一笑”的粉丝为见不到哥哥们疯狂流泪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/2d416a7eb6784e22b2d02a5919dd5c2d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然而没想到，更让他们悲痛欲绝的事情发生了：王一博恋情被锤！！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/8a61227906b74ff3b84a3e6af36b09aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">事情的一开始，是有人在飞机上拍到一个疑似王一博的人，他在翻看自己的聊天记录和手机图片。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/fba9e53a611b4cf49d1de2df8359ca84.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">为什么说疑似王一博呢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">第一是视频中的聊天背景图和王一博之前在微博上发过的自己的聊天背景图一样。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/fdd3b6a9a87d4dba990ca3e8375724e3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/89b9162d5dbb482cb1c535cf8c282e06.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/29a19d14c9184882b99330ca3ae6d0dc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">原图是一张杜宾犬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/0fd9d2273cb044b8ab43072b155e871d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">其次是手机中一张图片的背景是摩托车头盔墙，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/7c5bdc0047e14dff9393882beea0fbab.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">和王一博在天天向上秀过的很相似。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/6f35827043234457944b566da4a70dbb.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">第三是网友觉得，耍手机的大拇指弯曲弧度和指甲壳儿都很像王一博……（这届网友都姓福尔摩斯的吗？）</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/592b2574fc13441b97708078cb8c0bcb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/ec63be2972fe43feaf7115cb77db1906.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">以及视频里有一张疑似王一博的自拍照。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/80ef599e4cd64872ada0ebf4d547b738.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在网友的眼中，这些细节差不多锤死了就是王一博。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">那和恋情有什么关系呢？对象又是谁呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">网友又通过视频里的细节顺着网线摸到了疑似王一博的女友，綦美合，一个网红白富美。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/f7806eceadac405297de85a334c63c9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">首先是视频里聊天记录的头像和綦美合一样。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/635611780fe1408d8b57162631c3e0f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有疑似綦美合的图片。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/5d540f86391e48098cb869a0037d2f19.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">綦美合曾经在微博上发过的图片也被拍到在疑似王一博男子的手机里。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/aa431f72f550460085e74f023f79a38b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">而且网友还注意到这张图没有水印，应该是綦美合直接发给他的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/67a2715af37e41a7997abd13526a49c4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">视频里的细节就这么多，画质高糊也说不准个什么东西。爱哥如命的粉丝说视频中的是一个素人朋友，不过被素人朋友否认了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/974a2219a21749a987693317f0148088.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">于是网友立刻沸腾了，马上拿出放大镜找到了王一博和綦美合两人恋爱的蛛丝马迹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">比如他们ins很像情侣名，一个是emily. qi_一个是yibo. w_85，没加85的ID被别人注册过了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/f0bb0e98db69410390f830dcf2cc6613.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/083c71850de941e8854e01aa4145767e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">两个人暗戳戳的情侣款。（脚上的小花花）</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/fee5c140252643d48abf3f6ce84d7ede.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/b9a21ccb4c484e06ba8dc66993b4da0d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">两个人行程很对的上。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/11741deabedf4455b8cfc7c5a93eada1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/677497d8e3924b5c9dbf6b1a327eea56.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">甚至有人爆料当时站姐都是拉的两个人的行程单。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/4fa49b78633b41528d5b9b43b0e67b35.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/def37308a9e14706b0efbfea30731e6e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有两个人深夜吃鸡。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/c5766ebbd49f47bc9afc81eda17f501f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/dad58154be604d46afd5e8dc2a02ffc8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不过被乐华官方否认过了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/e14dc8c5902a46e1ad7c7a9e441108fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有王一博八月在天天向上说对女朋友的情话是“带回去，藏起来”，而七月綦美合的ins里面出现过粉丝集合评论的“带回去，藏起来”。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/51b1ae50f0cc49cf88f176b714761845.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有一些莫名其妙的知情人士爆料。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/9c0c2fdc3b644fa7a558f2847df06fe8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/f5870465aba44a5a81cd551c3a86c829.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/9a1137cc33934e3cac832a6fca416936.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">锤了这么多，很显然，綦美合马上该被人肉了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有人爆料说她是是耀莱集团老板的千金，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/84f9310fa462405d9325449c36009861.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">作为一个有钱的追星少女，她可以经常和一线流量接触，鹿晗、吴亦凡、欧阳娜娜、陈飞宇都和她有合照。</p>
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/18416ca5371a48c29fad084a43156f9f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/fad22130066442cd8105b3e208d643ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/d034e6a8823348aba3457e37291fe61c.jpeg" max-width="600"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/6c7961d09616465bb8111a09994c1036.jpeg" max-width="600" /></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">据说她还要去韩国当练习生，而且享受的都不是一般人的待遇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/e64bd9fed5d9454ebb3b05f536c08875.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/52e772f69cf44e97b87711f47fc4e055.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">她和华谊老总王中磊的女儿王文也是闺蜜，不过最近爆出的一组两人聊天记录有些败坏路人缘了，綦美合称普通人是“农民”。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/f08748a323ab4b169f885e2503a3b4f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">于是“陈立农”也被迫卷入了这场是非。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/e45053c1a9a6478b8f1351d4e85620aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大批网友在线种地。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/12d08ca93b514fe6bc35999e11c36706.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/a0696fdf86634a3e9404a9942bf0f5ce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/dc5381991a8b4cdabf2356ecaf0a55eb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这个锤我觉得有些可疑，毕竟一开始那个视频，不是在聊天，是有人在一张一张点开放大图片，甚至有人爆料是“王一博”故意的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190815/ee263f4eba78484584fd6a5f160c9934.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">明星故意曝恋情给私生饭？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这也太猛了？？？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">总之一些高糊的视频图片，如果想要伪造也不是难事，在官宣出来之前，我们还是别以讹传讹，安安静静地嗑嗑颜就好了~~</p>
